AD_Rule.Name: Medios Magnéticos - Formato 1002 - obtener vabo
AD_Rule.Script: import org.compiere.model.*; import org.compiere.util.*; import java.math.*; MElementValue ev = new MElementValue(A_Ctx, A_ConceptSource.getC_ElementValue_ID(), A_TrxName); String sql = "" + "SELECT Sum(iw.taxbaseamt * CASE " + " WHEN Substr(dt.docbasetype,3,3) = 'C' " + " THEN -1 " + " ELSE 1 " + " END) AS taxbaseamt " + "FROM lco_invoicewithholding iw " + " JOIN c_tax_acct ta " + " ON (ta.c_tax_id = iw.c_tax_id) " + " JOIN c_validcombination vc " + " ON (ta.t_credit_acct = vc.c_validcombination_id) " + " JOIN c_elementvalue ev " + " ON (vc.account_id = ev.c_elementvalue_id) " + " JOIN c_invoice i " + " ON (i.c_invoice_id = iw.c_invoice_id) " + " JOIN c_doctype dt " + " ON (i.c_doctype_id = dt.c_doctype_id) " + "WHERE i.ad_client_id = ? " + " AND iw.dateacct BETWEEN ? AND ? " + " AND i.issotrx = 'N' " + " AND iw.processed = 'Y' " + " AND iw.isactive = 'Y' " + " AND i.processed = 'Y' " + " AND i.isactive = 'Y' " + " AND ev.VALUE LIKE ? " + " AND i.c_bpartner_id = ?"; Object[] args = new Object[] { Env.getAD_Client_ID(A_Ctx), A_SendSchedule.getStartDate(), A_SendSchedule.getEndDate(), ev.getValue() + '%', A_C_BPartner_ID }; BigDecimal taxbaseamt = DB.getSQLValueBD(A_TrxName, sql, args); if (taxbaseamt != null && taxbaseamt instanceof BigDecimal) taxbaseamt.setScale(0, BigDecimal.ROUND_HALF_UP); else taxbaseamt = Env.ZERO; result = taxbaseamt;
